{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_05_03",
  "title": "fran 3話 どーんと一気に使いたかった",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the MV shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いい感じじゃないですか\nMVのセットにも、口を出した甲斐がありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ this looks good.\nIt was worth to mention about the MV set.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666667064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4333328645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ファッション業界の人間としては\n格好悪いセットで撮影するなんて、許せませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As someone in the fashion industry‚\nI can’t allow filming on an uncool set.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7999995311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "デザイン案は見てましたけど……\n組み上がってみると、だいぶ華やかになりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw the design plan…\nbut the set has become pretty flashy after assembled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7999995311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2333328645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ナチュラル風も悪くはないですけど\n私はギラギラで、格好いい方が好きなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Natural style isn’t bad‚\nbut I like glittery and cool things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9999995311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺もその方が、franさんらしい……\nいや、スリクスらしいクリスマスだと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also think that's more fit for fran-san's…\nNo‚ more fit for IIIX's Christmas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5333337546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1333341361
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1333341361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、セットだと分かってはいるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ I know it's a set‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.833326761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "綺麗なツリーとゴージャスなプレゼントに囲まれて\n最っ高の気分ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but being surrounded by a beautiful tree and gorgeous presents\nmakes me feel best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9999934276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……このプレゼントの山が現実だったら\nもっと良かったんですけどねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… It would be even better\nIf this mountain of presents were real.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2666634004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "あら。宝くじに当たったら、現実になりますよ？\n今の私、すっごいツキが来てると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ if I win the lottery‚ it will become reality.\nI think I'm super lucky right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2999974967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "さっき株価見たら、ホールドしてた株も上がってたし\nもうこれって絶対、一等が来る流れでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just checked the stock prices‚ and the stocks I have went up.\nThis is definitely a sign that I'm going to win first prize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1999964794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "そうなったら、{user}さんにも\n何か奢ってあげますよ。楽しみにしてて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that happens‚ for {user}-san‚\nI will treat you to something. Look forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8333282869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、楽しみですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6666616202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そして、年末",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――And‚ the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6333282869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 76.7333303214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、お願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ go ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9999807122,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4000.013693,
          "startTime": 81.9999944052
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "では、一等から当選番号読み上げますね\n一等が81組の128347番、二等が138組の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I’ll read out the winning numbers starting from first place.\nFirst prize is group 81 number 128347‚ second prize is group 138…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9333089593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "三等、組番号の下一桁は7、141954番\n四等、下四桁が1890番……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Third prize‚ last digit of the group number is 7‚ number 141954\nFourth prize‚ last four digits are 1890…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5333130283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "……嘘でしょ。どこにも入ってない\n七等にもかすってないって、どういうことよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re kidding. It's not anywhere.\nHow is this possible‚ it didn't even scratch 7th place!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2666422926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、まぁ\n宝くじに当たるかどうかは、結局、運ですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I mean‚\nWhether you win the lottery or not is all a matter of luck…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5666422926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "あんなにツキが来てたのに！！\n絶対、当たると思ったのにっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so lucky!!\nI thought I was definitely going to win…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1999649449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……懸賞とか信号で\n貯めておいたツキを、使い切ってしまったんですかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Could it be because you spent all your luck\nfor giveaways and traffic lights?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6666372064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく、あんな頑張って貯めたんだから\nもっと大きく、どーんと一気に使いたかった！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I worked so hard to save it up‚\nso I wanted to spend it all in one big go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.533295735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、徳を積もうとしたのが間違いだったわ\n私としたことが、あんなオカルトに騙されるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a mistake to try and accumulate virtue in the first place.\nI can’t believe I was fooled by that occult stuff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5999624017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "善いことをするのは別に問題ないんじゃ……\nそういえば、俺は今回ちょっとだけツイてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not a problem to do good deeds…\nCome to think of it‚ I was a little lucky this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.8332937005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "え、{user}さんだけってどういうこと\n一体、どんなラッキーがあったっていうんです！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Why was only {user}-san lucky?\nWhat kind of luck did you get!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2666270338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "franさんがアイドルを辞めないでくれましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you didn’t quit being an idol‚ fran-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0999603672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "本当に宝くじに当たったらどうしようかと思ってたんで\nだから……まぁ、ツイてたなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was wondering what I would do if you actually won the lottery.\nSo… yeah‚ I guess I was lucky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.0999522291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに気にしてたんですか？\nさすがに、いきなり仕事を投げ出したりはしませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you worried about that?\nI don’t suddenly quit my job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.5332855625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "それに、前に言ったでしょ\nファッションの次くらいにはアイドルも好きだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ I told you before\nthat I like being an idol almost as much as fashion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.4332947178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "……っていうか、よく考えたら\n私が外れるように祈ってたってことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait a second‚ that means\nYou were hoping I wouldn’t win!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6999603672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "わ、悪気はなかったんです！\nでもスリクスのファンのことも考えないとですね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ I didn’t mean anything bad by it!\nbut we have to think about IIIX fans too!?",
        "id": ""
