    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　このリップ！\n前から気になってたけど、買う機会なかったんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! This lipstick!\nI’ve been wanting this for a while‚ but I haven't had the chance to buy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.7665873608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "当選金ってほどじゃないですけど\nでも、少しでもいいことがあって良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not like prize money‚\nbut I’m glad something good happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.5332377515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor024.m4a",
      "text": "一銭も入らないまま、年越しなんて\nちょっと悲し過ぎますし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would’ve been too sad\nto start the new year without getting a single penny…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.8332296135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、善いことをしてたから\nきっとサンタがプレゼントを持ってきてくれたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See? Because you did good deeds‚\nSanta must have brought you a present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.1665629468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor025.m4a",
      "text": "うわ、寒っ。私は大人なので拾ってあげますけど\nそれ、他の子の前で言わない方がいいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ it’s cold. Since I’m an adult‚ so I’ll pick it up for you‚\nbut you shouldn’t say that in front of the other girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.899899332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor026.m4a",
      "text": "中高生くらいの子には、寒い冗談言うおじさんなんて\n最悪なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For middle and high school girls‚ an old man making corny jokes\nis the worst.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.6665659986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_03-kor027.m4a",
      "text": "はあ～……\nあ～あ、来年もあいつらと一緒にアイドル活動か～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…\nAh~ ah‚ guess I'll be doing idol activities with those two next year too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.3998972974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
